"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The code incorrectly sets the x-axis ticks and labels. The `set_xticks` and `set_xticklabels` methods are not necessary when using `MonthLocator` and `DateFormatter`. Additionally, `ax` is being reassigned after the seaborn plot, which can cause issues.\",\n  \"patch\": \"14c14\\n< fig, ax = plt.subplots()\\n---\\n> fig, ax = plt.subplots()\\n16,17d15\\n< ax.set_xticks(df.date.unique())\\n< ax.set_xticklabels(labels=df.date.unique(), rotation=45)\\n\"\n}"